meanings: (하고 싶다) (동사로 쓰여) want (to), would like to, wish (to), (formal) desire (to), feel like (doing)
(~한 생각이 들다) (동사로 쓰여) look, seem, appear
감정 There is no need for me to hear it.
감정 That's the end of it.
질문과 대답 I don't want to answer that.
질문과 대답 I'd rather not answer that.
질문과 대답 I don't owe you any explanations.

meanings.meaning: rather you, him, etc. than me
go through the motions (of doing something)
